&lt;p&gt;Having a &lt;strong&gt;pending transaction&lt;/strong&gt; can be quite annoying
and usually happens when the network is heavy loaded and the fees are
sky rocketing. Your transaction may have a &lt;strong&gt;too low gas
fee&lt;/strong&gt; and miner are just ignoring it to prefer others transaction
with higher fees.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This result in you being stuck because until that transaction is
resolved you cannot send any other transaction. Annoying right ?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Let’s dive right in on how to fix this !&lt;/p&gt;
